Three Bungoma woman representative aspirants have urged other women to vie for elective posts. They are Cathrine Wambilainga (Ford Kenya), Antonina Sangura (UDP) and Nancy Kibaba (Ford Kenya).Kibaba, the nominated MCA representing the youth, said women have proven to be good leaders who can serve the community diligently.They spoke in Mayuba Stadium during celebrations to mark International Women's Day on Wednesday.